WEBVTT

00:00:01.500 --> 00:00:04.600
If I used one sentence to describe the last season
如果用一句话去表达上一集的话

00:00:04.600 --> 00:00:10.533
It might be "taking the first step" or "searching for the unknown"
可能是迈出第一步或者是寻找未知

00:00:12.133 --> 00:00:14.466
For Season 2, I think it is "choice"
第二次的话我觉得是选择

00:00:15.533 --> 00:00:17.166
Choosing which route?
选择哪条线路

00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:19.700
yes 
耶

00:00:19.733 --> 00:00:22.966
Choosing to continue climbing, or choosing to descend
选择继续攀爬还是选择下降哦哈哈哈

00:00:23.033 --> 00:00:24.800
Inhale  exhale
吸气呼吸

00:00:24.800 --> 00:00:27.100
Or choose a direction in life. It`s all about choices
或者选择生活方向都是选择

00:00:27.133 --> 00:00:29.600
Do you trust this stopper（protection gear） ?
这个塞子你比较信任嘛

00:00:29.666 --> 00:00:31.300
I don't really trust any of them
每个都不太信任

00:00:31.333 --> 00:00:35.033
So I'm also thinking. which thing will I choose
所以我也在想到底哪个事情我会去选择

00:00:35.033 --> 00:00:37.600
Or what is worth my focused effort.
或者是值得我去专注的做

00:00:37.666 --> 00:00:38.966
Good ?
OK 了吗

00:00:39.033 --> 00:00:40.200
I don't know
不知道呀

00:00:41.433 --> 00:00:44.266
Maybe found the general meaning
可能找到了大概的意义

00:00:44.300 --> 00:00:46.033
Maybe it is just searching for vitality
可能就是在寻找生命力吧

00:00:46.200 --> 00:00:47.533
Ah, it's a bit high.
啊 有点高啊

00:00:47.566 --> 00:00:52.000
Maybe it is that I want to challenge myself and stimulate my own nerves
可能就是我要去挑战刺激我自己的神经

00:00:52.066 --> 00:00:53.533
Well done
做的好

00:00:54.666 --> 00:00:57.300
So for Season two, I'm going rock climbing.
所以第二季我要去攀岩哦

00:00:57.333 --> 00:00:58.366
Hard to step on
不好踩

00:00:58.433 --> 00:01:01.800
Maybe climbing is challenging yourself at every single moment
可能攀岩在无时无刻的一直在挑战自己

00:01:02.800 --> 00:01:05.133
The start is really hard
起步真的很难

00:01:06.300 --> 00:01:09.733
And breaking through my own difficulties that attracts me more
然后突破自己的困难会比较吸引我

00:01:12.133 --> 00:01:15.433
I feel climbing is a way of finding oneself.
我觉得攀岩是寻找自我的一种方式

00:01:15.500 --> 00:01:17.533
Constantly exploring new realms
不断的探索心境吧

00:01:18.633 --> 00:01:20.400
Living life to the extreme
活出生命的极致